	<!--# The "user_remove_all_bindings" field specifies whether to unregister the phone, when requested to reboot, for example. Valid values are "on"==Unregister On Reboot, "off"==Do Not Unregister On Reboot. The provisioning template sets the value to "on"==Unregister On Reboot.-->
    <user_remove_all_bindings idx="1" perm="">off</user_remove_all_bindings>

